<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2156/98 of 7 October 1998 derogating from Regulation (EC) No 1223/94 laying down special detailed rules for the application of the system of advance-fixing certificates for certain agricultural products exported in the form of goods not covered by Annex II to the Treaty as regards the period of validity of the advance-fixing certificates for sugar </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 2156/98, milles s&auml;testatakse seoses suhkru eelkinnitussertifikaatide kehtivusajaga erand m&auml;&auml;rusest (E&Uuml;) nr 1223/94, milles s&auml;testatakse &uuml;ksikasjalikud erieeskirjad teatavate asutamislepingu II lisas loetlemata kaupadena eksporditavate p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete eelkinnitussertifikaatide s&uuml;steemi kohaldamiseks 7. oktoober 1998 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 3448/93 of 6 December 1993 laying down the trade arrangements applicable to certain goods resulting from the processing of agricultural products (1), as amended by Regulation (EC) No 1097/98 (2), and in particular the first subparagraph of Article 8(3) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 6. detsembri 1993. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 3448/93 p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisel saadud teatavate kaupadega kauplemise korra kohta, (1) muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1097/98, (2) eelk&otilde;ige selle artikli 8 l&otilde;ike 3 esimest l&otilde;iku, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation (EC) No 1223/94 of 30 May 1994 laying down special detailed rules for the application of the system of advance-fixing certificates for certain agricultural products exported in the form of goods not covered by Annex II to the Treaty (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1479/98 (4), stipulates that the advance-fixing certificates for sugar shall be valid until the end of the fifth month following that of issue; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: komisjoni 30. mai 1994. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruses (E&Uuml;) nr 1223/94, milles s&auml;testatakse &uuml;ksikasjalikud erieeskirjad teatavate asutamislepingu II lisas loetlemata kaupadena eksporditavate p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete eelkinnitussertifikaatide s&uuml;steemi kohaldamiseks, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1479/98, (4) s&auml;testatakse, et suhkru puhul kehtivad eelkinnitussertifikaadid nende v&auml;ljastamisele j&auml;rgneva viienda kuu l&otilde;puni; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the situation on the world market in sugar is particularly volatile, the refund levels are particularly high at present and it is hard to predict what price trends will be, particularly over the entire current period of validity of the certificates; </inglise>
<eesti> maailma suhkruturu olukord on eriti ebastabiilne, toetusm&auml;&auml;rad on k&otilde;rged ja hinnasuundumusi on raske ette n&auml;ha, eelk&otilde;ige kogu sertifikaatide kehtivusaja jooksul; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the refund levels substantially increase the level of expenditure on agricultural products exported in the form of non-Annex II goods with the danger of subsequently reducing the prospects for exporting these products, in accordance with the international agreements concluded by the Community; whereas, consequently, steps must be taken to avoid aggravating these consequences by excessive recourse to advance fixing of the refund rates; whereas, under these conditions, the period of validity of these advance-fixing certificates should be limited, temporarily, to until the end of the third month following that of issue; </inglise>
<eesti> toetuse m&auml;&auml;rad suurendavad oluliselt II lisas nimetamata toodetena v&auml;ljaveetavate p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete suhtes tehtavaid kulutusi, mis v&otilde;ib oluliselt v&auml;hendada nende toodete eksportimise v&otilde;imalusi vastavalt &uuml;henduse s&otilde;lmitud rahvusvahelistele lepingutele; sellest tulenevalt tuleks v&otilde;tta meetmeid, et v&auml;ltida nende tagaj&auml;rgede s&uuml;venemist toetusm&auml;&auml;rade liiga sagedase eelneva kinnitamise teel; niisugustes tingimustes tuleks eelkinnitussertifikaatide kehtivusaega ajutiselt piirata nende v&auml;ljastamisele j&auml;rgneva kolmanda kuu l&otilde;puni; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for horizontal questions concerning trade in processed agricultural products not listed in Annex II, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las II lisas loetlemata t&ouml;&ouml;deldud p&otilde;llumajandussaadustega kauplemist puudutavaid horisontaalk&uuml;simusi k&auml;sitleva korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> By way of derogation from Article 4(1) of Regulation (EC) No 1223/94, the advance-fixing certificates for products covered by the common organisation of the market in sugar shall be valid until the end of the third month following that of issue. </inglise>
<eesti> Erandina m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 1223/94 artikli 4 l&otilde;ikest 1 kehtivad suhkruturu &uuml;hise korraldusega h&otilde;lmatud toodete eelkinnitussertifikaadid nende v&auml;ljastamisele j&auml;rgneva kolmanda kuu l&otilde;puni. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> It shall apply to applications for certificates lodged from 1 October 1998. </inglise>
<eesti> Seda kohaldatakse p&auml;rast 1. oktoobrit 1998 esitatavate sertifikaaditaotluste suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 7 October 1998. </inglise>
